en_721372_0	Brigadier Lalith Rathnayake of Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment assumed duties as the new General Officer Commanding, 51 Division on Monday (8) in a simple ceremony.
en_721372_1	The newly-appointed GOC was greeted to a Guard Turnout and a Guard of Honour parade upon his arrival at the premises.
en_721372_2	Subsequently, the GOC signed a formal documents to signify the acceptance his new office amid religious observances.
en_721372_3	He also was invited to plant a sapling as a simple of memory.
en_721372_4	Senior military Officers, Divisional Staff Officers, Officers and Other Ranks were present at the venue.
